      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Canahya tlaixpan quence ce cuecuetztzin tzacualli campa nochipa quichihuah ce tlamantli, campa monehpanoah ohmeh huan tianquiz tlen nochi Mesoamerica.</Note_Text>
